        <small>Required fields marked with <span style="color:var(--brand-red); font-weight:700">*</span>. Greyed-out options are not selectable with your current configuration. See the legend in the Optional column for <span style="color:var(--text-primary); font-weight:700">★</span> / QS / MTO meanings.</small>
